{"tid":742010,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 睡房分體式冷氣結冰","createTime":"2018-07-14T07:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T15:46:20.000Z","uid":73158,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7f3b94ec4707ae5ee4acb2523f7c6c0b00420fa2","tid":742010,"uid":73158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"琴晚開開冷房，聽到部機有怪聲，我拆開佢黎睇，內面結哂冰。<br />\n我琴晚剷起哂d雪，等佢解反凍啦，我頭先開機正常已無怪聲。<br />\n咁我諗住搞掂啦，點鳩知又結返冰。<br />\n<br />\n有無冷氣高手可以解答下我，部機仲有無得搞？定係一定要換？仲有我睇唔到出面部機同埋我揾/睇唔到會唔會係條喉塞左，因為d喉入哂牆。<br />\n<br />\n有諗過揾師傅上黎睇我又怕佢蝦我唔識hea 9 我。<br />\n<br />\n希望有高手入黎俾d建議我，萬般感激<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一幅相係琴晚剷雪前<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/154254_9c1c8112db212fe302e396e169b32dca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F154254_9c1c8112db212fe302e396e169b32dca.png&h=ba6015fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依幅係無雪後，過左晚，再開機後情況，其實佢依家已經又白哂，有層雪起度<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/154418_ecfadcd251cb3f9e60a3a3ddedc126b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F154418_ecfadcd251cb3f9e60a3a3ddedc126b8.png&h=38463060&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"383a66a7134621df65b689cb4da0c8fdfd577a1f","tid":742010,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"去水唔好，通下條去水管同清下D垃圾（洗機）理論上可以頂到一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a755be67e54ae42f027d43d6c901662c68bd747","tid":742010,"uid":73158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383a66a7134621df65b689cb4da0c8fdfd577a1f","tid":742010,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"去水唔好，通下條去水管同清下D垃圾（洗機）理論上可以頂到一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"巴打，條喉大機會起邊？因為d野入哂埸，我完全無頭緒點che